1) Follow pu_README to produce pileup root files for data

2) Use the correct input array from step 1) and put it in 
   standalone_LumiReWeighting.cc

3) Make sure standalone_LumiReWeighting.* are in the same  
  directory as  puweight_sys.*

4) Run puweight_sys on 
   /data2/syu/zjet_vectorNtuple/pu_reweigh_DYJetsToLL_TuneZ2_M-50_7TeV-madgraph-tauola.root

5) Use getPUSysRange.C to get the range of PU correction and 
   systematic uncertainty.

   This script will produce myPUSys.root that saves the correction  
   factor and ratios of systematic shift to the central value.


6) Use plotPUCorr.C and plotPUSys.C to fit the correction and 
   systematic uncertainties





